Usage: read_stream [-help] -layer_map <string> {[-pvs_fill ] | [[<in_files>] [-cells <string> [-offset {x y}]]]}

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
<in_files>              # GDS and OASIS file list (list, optional)
-cells <string>         # Only read in the specified cells from gds files.
                        # (string, optional)
-layer_map <string>     # layer map file map GDS layer to design layer
                        # (string, required)
-offset {x y}           # -offset x y (point, optional)
-pvs_fill               # PVS FILL data need to be processed in read process
                        # (bool, optional)